Feature Put selected chair to the shopping basket
Description: This Feature will test the functionality of how to put the selected item in the shopping basket 

Scenario: User can find the product category
  Given www.baldai1.lt page is opened
  When User press "Visi baldai"
  And Press "Kedes"
  Then The list of all chairs are listed in the page

Scenario: User can select the chair from the list
  Given Scenario 1 should be completed
  When User press first cair in the page 
  Then the selected chair page is opened

Scenario: USer can add selected chiar in the basket
  Given Scenario 2 should be completed
  When user press "Į krepšelį"
  Then the selected cair is added to the basket
